1   package org.hibernate.testing.cache;
2   
3   import org.hibernate.cache.CacheException;
4   import org.hibernate.cache.spi.access.SoftLock;
5   
6   /**
7    * @author Strong Liu <stliu@hibernate.org>
8    */
9   class TransactionalEntityRegionAccessStrategy extends BaseEntityRegionAccessStrategy {
10  	TransactionalEntityRegionAccessStrategy(EntityRegionImpl region) {
11  		super( region );
12  	}
13  
14  	/**
15  	 * {@inheritDoc}
16  	 */
17  	public boolean afterInsert(Object key, Object value, Object version) {
18  		return false;
19  	}
20  
21  	/**
22  	 * {@inheritDoc}
23  	 */
24  	public boolean afterUpdate(Object key, Object value, Object currentVersion, Object previousVersion, SoftLock lock) {
25  		return false;
26  	}
27  
28  
29  	/**
30  	 * {@inheritDoc}
31  	 */
32  	@Override
33  	public void remove(Object key) throws CacheException {
34  		evict( key );
35  	}
36  
37  
38  	/**
39  	 * {@inheritDoc}
40  	 */
41  	public boolean update(Object key, Object value, Object currentVersion,
42  						  Object previousVersion) throws CacheException {
43  		return insert( key, value, currentVersion );
44  	}
45  }
